PROD_NAME: VM:Manager Common Components (VMAN, VMAIM, VMAIC, VMGRW)

SRC_PHYS_LOC: Source resides on DEV DASD packs.;The GA releases of the datasets are stored on DEVR volumes which are tier-1 backed up DASD volumes.   For the pre-beta and BETA releases;the datasets are allocated on DEV volumes which are not part of DR.    When the products are moved into GA;the datasets are moved to the DEVR volumes.
